* seems like they really shorten the range for the /stick command after patch -- not sure why was done, but i find it a disappointing downgrade on a very useful feature ... may be mythic still tweaking it /shrug ... the /follow function still needs work i think too<br>
<br>
* leading a full group of 8 people is really a challenge... esp when all are strangers who have never played with one another...  and most people i think are still learning the gameplay and their class the strengths and weaknesses.  ... but when the 8 people really click, it is really a wonderful feeling<br>
<br>
* north of ardee, before the bridge -- to the northwest, tehre are lots of wind ghouls... blue and green at level 10 -- great soloing place, and i think should be a great group place at level 8ish if anyone looking for fresh new, uncrowded region to hunt in.<br>
<br>
*quest -- try to do them... esp the ones given out by your class trainer.  did my level 7 and got wonderful neckpiece +3str +2 hits.  the quests in general are highly rewarding and worthwhile to do.<br>
<br>
just my 2 cps... a couple observations i noticed playing the game... or mayhap it is the meandering mind of a tired man... anyways have fun all 8-)<br>
<br>
